K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-022:133a-4: ma bsgrubs kyang las thams cad 'grub par 'gyur te gi wang la lan brgya rtsa brgyad bzlas nas dpral bar thig le byas na gang bltas pa de dga' bar 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-022:133a-5: mig rtsi la lan brgya rtsa brgyad sngags te mig la bskus na gang dang phrad par bya ba de dga' bar 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-022:133a-6: chu khyor gang la lan bdun bzlas te 'thungs na ma bslangs par zas rnyed par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-022:133a-7: tshogs pa'i nang du 'gro na bdag gi gos kyi mtha' ma nas lag pa g-yon pas bzung la lan nyi shu rtsa gcig bzlas brjod byas nas tshogs pa'i nang du song na tshig btsan par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-022:133a-8: tshig btsan pa'i gzungs rdzogs so ////
